text.tspan: Borrowing to start or expand business, men vs women, 2014
Percentage of men and women (ages 15+) who report borrowing any money in the past 12 months (by themselves
or together with someone else) to start, operate, or expand a farm or business. Colors represent world regions.
Bubble sizes are proportional to the population of the country.
